OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FA number of events have been cancelled
OL,7,Facross Kent as the county continues to
OL,8,Fdeal with an outbreak of meningitis.
OL,10,FSports fixtures and other events have
OL,11,Fbeen postponed or called off as safety
OL,12,Fconcerns are raised.
OL,14,FThe Kent Disability Football League
OL,15,Fhas confirmed that a tournament due to
OL,16,Fbe held this weekend has been called
OL,17,Foff so no-one is put at risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
