OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773933104
OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FPosting on Facebook a spokesperson for
OL,7,Fthe league committee said: "I am
OL,8,Fwriting to inform you that the Kent
OL,9,FDisability Football League committee
OL,10,Fhas made the difficult decision to
OL,11,Fcancel this Sunday's Junior Section
OL,12,Ftournament.
OL,14,F"This decision follows recent reports
OL,15,Fregarding an outbreak of meningitis.
OL,16,FWhile we understand the disappointment
OL,17,Fthis may cause our young players, the
OL,18,Fsafety, health, and well-being of our
OL,19,Fparticipants, their families, and our
OL,20,Fvolunteers remain our absolute
OL,21,Fpriority.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773933104
OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"Given the nature of the situation, we
OL,7,Fbelieve a cautious approach is the
OL,8,Fonly responsible course of action to
OL,9,Fensure we are not putting any members
OL,10,Fof our community at risk.
OL,12,F"We appreciate your understanding and
OL,13,Fcooperation in helping us keep the
OL,14,FKDFL community safe. If you have any
OL,15,Fimmediate questions, please do not
OL,16,Fhesitate to reach out to the
OL,17,Fcommittee."
OL,19,FTraining sessions for all of St
OL,20,FLawrence and Highland Court Cricket
OL,21,FClub have been cancelled this week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
