OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773933104
OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FA spokesperson said the decision is a
OL,7,Fprecautionary measure and the safety
OL,8,Fand wellbeing of members is 'a top
OL,9,Fpriority'.
OL,11,FCanterbury parkrun which is held at
OL,12,Fthe university campus has been
OL,13,Fcancelled on Saturday. (21 March)
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the weekly event
OL,16,Fsaid: "We are sorry to announce that
OL,17,Four parkrun on 21 March 2026 has been
OL,18,Fcancelled.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
