CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773933104
OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"It would be inappropriate to
OL,7,Fcelebrate our anniversary given the
OL,8,Funfortunate events currently impacting
OL,9,Fthe staff and students at the
OL,10,FUniversity.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts are with the families
OL,13,Fand friends of all those affected by
OL,14,Fthe meningitis outbreak."
OL,16,FIt's not just sports events which have
OL,17,Fbeen called off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
