OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FHighparks Medical Practice which is
OL,7,Fbased in Rochester has decided to
OL,8,Fcancel its training sessions on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FA post on their Facebook page said:
OL,12,F"Today's PLT (Protected Learning Time)
OL,13,Fsessions scheduled for this afternoon
OL,14,Fhave been cancelled by the ICB due to
OL,15,Fthe ongoing meningitis situation and
OL,16,Fincreased demand and contact to
OL,17,Fpractices.
OL,19,F"Practices across Medway have been
OL,20,Fasked to remain open this afternoon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
