OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773933104
OL,3,CEvents cancelled across Kent as county
OL,4,Ccontinues to battle meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"As a result, we currently have
OL,7,Favailable nurse clinic appointments.
OL,9,F"If you are waiting for a blood test
OL,10,F(as requested by a clinician) or any
OL,11,Fnurse/HCA appointment - even if it is
OL,12,Fbooked for a later date, and would
OL,13,Flike to bring it forward to today,
OL,14,Fplease contact us.
OL,16,F"We will do our best to accommodate
OL,17,Fyou based on availability."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
